sequenceDiagram
    participant WS as WebScanner
    participant CP as check_path()
    participant REQ as requests 库
    participant SS as 会话 / 适配器
    participant DNS as DNS 解析
    participant NET as 目标服务器

    WS->>CP: check_path(path)
    CP->>CP: url = urljoin(target_url, path)

    rect rgb(235, 235, 235)
        Note over CP,NET: requests.get() 请求流程
        CP->>REQ: requests.get(url, timeout, headers, allow_redirects)
        REQ->>REQ: 构建 Request 对象
        REQ->>SS: Session.send(PreparedRequest)
        SS->>SS: 创建 TCP 连接
        SS->>DNS: 解析域名 → IP 地址
        DNS-->>SS: 返回 IP
        SS->>NET: 建立 TCP 连接 (三次握手)
        NET-->>SS: 连接建立
        SS->>NET: 发送 HTTP GET 请求
        Note right of NET: GET /path HTTP/1.1<br/>Host: target<br/>User-Agent: ListScanner/2.0
        NET-->>SS: 返回 HTTP 响应
        Note left of SS: HTTP/1.1 status_code<br/>Content-Type<br/>Content-Length
        SS-->>REQ: Response 对象
        REQ-->>CP: response
    end

    alt 请求成功
        CP->>CP: response.status_code == 404?
        alt status == 404
            CP-->>WS: (None, "not_found")
        else status != 404
            CP->>CP: check_risk(path) → (risk_type, risk_level)
            CP->>CP: 构建 ScanResult(path, url, status_code, size, content_type, risk_type, risk_level)
            CP-->>WS: (ScanResult, "found")
        end
    else requests.RequestException (超时/连接拒绝/DNS失败)
        CP-->>WS: (None, "error")
    end
